===Pronunciation===
שׁרץ / shârats / shaw-rats'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''שׁרץ'''

# To [[wriggle]], that is, (by implication) [[swarm]] or [[abound]]: - [[breed]] (bring forth, increase) [[abundantly]] (in [[abundance]]), [[creep]], [[move]].

